Class AttributeNotFoundException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class AttributeNotFoundException
extends java.lang.Exception
    Exception cast when requrested XML attribute (its value) can't be found or resolving reference to global (TransformationGraph level) variable/property can't be done - the property key is not present.
    See Also:
    Exception, Serialized Form
